Install info for cppnow, a TDD tutorial in C++

Download and install CMake (see separate file)

Download and install boost:
sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev

Download and install Turtle Mock:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/turtle/

You can also refer to the slides for this presentation when you find them in the Git repo.
Follow the link from the README in the root of the repo.
